{
  "stem": "9091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was their official explanation later, from what I understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they took them all, and they took them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to stop every so often and get some [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] hot soup and some provisions and water [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] supply in, in every car.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we might have stopped-- I don't know-- some places hours, some places maybe days, or some places maybe only overnight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, those are details that as a child I can't tell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess to me at that time, time wasn't something to measure, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they-- we-- it took us a, a long time until we reached our destination and, and they took us off the train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess we were taken to a place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I guess, where we got off was Novosibirsk, a place that's a, a town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Novosibirsk, that's the capital of that region.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from there, we were taken by all kind of transportation to some villages deeper in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] In Siberia we had very bad conditions, very bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Food was in very short supply.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my mother and my brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Food was in very short supply.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many people were with money so they could help themselves this way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could buy some product, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] food, bread, some-- they were some Russian people that they were living there in that, in the village, and they had their own fields so they had potatoes and all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had meat, pigs that they would sell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was for money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since we didn't have money, we couldn't buy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
